 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
                    Dividend     % growth       Pre-tax       % growth
                        year         from     profit year         from
                    to March         year      to March           year
                    1993 (p)      earlier   1993 (Pounds m)    earlier
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
Southern             19.6          17.65         187.0           12.45
London               19.5          16.07         145.5            2.11
Midlands               20          15.94         167.1           17.59
Seeboard               20          15.94         112.7           14.53
