<HEADLINE>
FT  10 JUL 93 / The G7 Summit: Uruguay Round deal 'top priority'
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By PETER NORMAN, Economics Editor
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   TOKYO
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
