<HEADLINE>
FT  09 JUL 93 / Building listings
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
THE GOVERNMENT has proposed a more selective approach to listing buildings.
It said priority should be on identifying the best examples of particular
types of buildings under-represented on the list.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
